body_html:
Hi again,

Issue solved, I found out that when I ran it in python it worked --> so something wrong in my conda environment. The ipython I ran was the one that was installed in the root environment. So when I installed it in the tfcuda9.1 environment, it worked! Very happy running the newest of the newest! thanks for all the work!

Best,

Hanneke
